Class GasStationManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inrix.sdk.AreaLimitedManager
      • com.inrix.sdk.GasStationManager

  • public class GasStationManager
extends AreaLimitedManager
    Manages the asynchronous retrieval of gas station information.
